headline: Lennar (LEN) Tops Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Lennar (LEN) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 22.99% and 1.61%, respectively, for the quarter ended February 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: North American Construction (NOA) Lags Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: North American Construction (NOA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.74% and 0.93%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
